title: AMV Hell Ultimate Collection (Jan 30, 2015)
description:
As of Jan 30, 2015, this torrent contains all AMV Hell and AMV Minis content that has been released,
with the exception of AMV Hell 0 and AMV Hell / 0. These two are X rated and can be downloaded seperately.
If more content is released in the future, this torrent will be updated, so just check http://www.amvhell.com

Regarding AMV Minis Challenge, in order to understand the context behind each episode, I highly recommend 
viewing the following page before watching: http://www.amvhell.com/showthread.php?27304

The majority of content in AMV Hell and AMV Minis is roughly equivalent to that of a PG-13 film, with a few exceptions. 
The following videos may contain adult language and/or nudity which may be inappropriate for younger viewers:
- AMV Hell 2
- AMV Hell Championship Edition
- AMV Minis X2 - Bad Stuff
- AMV Minis S2 X3 - Bad Stuff 2
- AMV Minis S2 X4 - Live Action
These files have been marked with (17+) in the filename.

For a list of credits of all of the sources used in these videos, 
or to submit your own videos for any current or future projects,
please check http://www.amvhell.com
